    </edge>
    <data key="d0">TASOLS Event-Driven Serverless Machine Learning Architecture</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GJ1So_pbZWk</data>
    <data key="d2">TASOLS provides advanced analytics and data science using machine learning. The architecture is a fully serverless, event-driven solution designed for chaining multiple machine learning models. It supports various data sources, performs ETL, and delivers insights ('Next Best Offer') via real-time API and BI dashboards. The solution was previously on EC2 but moved to serverless for better automation and productionization.</data>
    <data key="d3">data_ingestion, compute_intensive, interactive</data>
    <data key="d4">True</data>
  </graph>
</graphml>
